          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1680534448245-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> tomato paste </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>in 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[110ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1680534453729-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1680534453729-x400.jpg",
